264
00:12:32,125 --> 00:12:34,000
[RIMURU]
I did it, Shizu.

265
00:12:34,083 --> 00:12:35,750
Your students are safe.

266
00:12:38,041 --> 00:12:40,416
And we all lived
happily ever after.

267
00:12:40,500 --> 00:12:41,916
[laughs]
Psyche.

268
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:44,958
Actually, I still owed Ramiris
a replacement

269
00:12:45,041 --> 00:12:47,416
for the golem
I kinda sorta destroyed.

270
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:48,958
♪

271
00:12:51,791 --> 00:12:53,583
Of course the golem
was just a shell,

272
00:12:53,666 --> 00:12:56,666
so then I had to summon
a demon to possess it.

273
00:12:56,750 --> 00:12:59,916
And there would be
one last struggle.

274
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:02,666
But that's a story
for another time.

275
00:13:05,416 --> 00:13:07,166
I can't thank you enough,
Rimuru.

276
00:13:07,250 --> 00:13:10,458
[RIMURU chuckles]
No thanks necessary, my dude.

277
00:13:10,541 --> 00:13:13,041
I'm just glad the kids are okay.

278
00:13:13,125 --> 00:13:15,708
They should be able to lead
normal lives now, right?

279
00:13:15,791 --> 00:13:18,333
Yes. It's highly unlikely
the nations

280
00:13:18,416 --> 00:13:20,333
who abandoned them
will try to take them back.

281
00:13:20,416 --> 00:13:23,875
And it'd violate
international law.

282
00:13:23,958 --> 00:13:25,958
They would be making enemies
out of the Free Union

283
00:13:26,041 --> 00:13:27,458
if they did try that.

284
00:13:27,541 --> 00:13:29,875
[RIMURU] Are you planning
on giving the kids IDs

285
00:13:29,958 --> 00:13:31,750
and making them
members of the Union?

286
00:13:31,833 --> 00:13:33,833
Who knows?

287
00:13:33,916 --> 00:13:36,000
It's not a bad idea
if that's what they want.

288
00:13:36,083 --> 00:13:37,500
So it's certainly a possibility.

289
00:13:38,500 --> 00:13:40,875
For right now, I'd like to
let them continue studying

290
00:13:40,958 --> 00:13:44,500
at Freedom Academy and give them
a choice about their futures.

291
00:13:44,583 --> 00:13:45,958
[RIMURU]
Yeah, that sounds cool.

292
00:13:46,041 --> 00:13:48,625
They're in good hands.

293
00:13:48,708 --> 00:13:52,041
I wanted to ask.
How did you pull it all off?

294
00:13:52,125 --> 00:13:53,750
Like, how did you save them?

295
00:13:53,833 --> 00:13:56,291
[RIMURU laughs]
That's a trade secret.

296
00:13:56,375 --> 00:13:58,583
Some things are just
better off not knowing.

297
00:13:58,666 --> 00:14:01,625
And while it probably doesn't
make up for not telling you,

298
00:14:01,708 --> 00:14:04,333
here is a consolation prize.

299
00:14:04,416 --> 00:14:05,333
[grunts]

300
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:07,916
[YUUKI]
This is awesome!

301
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:10,166
Thank you so much, Rimuru!

302
00:14:12,708 --> 00:14:14,375
[KIDS laughing]

303
00:14:15,708 --> 00:14:17,625
[indistinct playful chatter]

304
00:14:17,708 --> 00:14:18,833
[KENYA]
Hey, wait for me!

305
00:14:18,916 --> 00:14:20,333
-[RANGA grunts, pants]
-[KIDS laughing]

306
00:14:20,416 --> 00:14:22,000
[ALICE]
We're coming!

307
00:14:22,083 --> 00:14:23,625
[KIDS laughing]

308
00:14:25,416 --> 00:14:27,375
♪

309
00:14:29,166 --> 00:14:32,458
[RIMURU] So much has happened
since I came to this world.

310
00:14:58,375 --> 00:15:02,791
♪

311
00:16:23,291 --> 00:16:26,625
♪

312
00:17:37,208 --> 00:17:39,750
But now it's over.
They're safe.

313
00:17:39,833 --> 00:17:41,750
All of our problems
are resolved.

314
00:17:41,833 --> 00:17:43,708
[wind blowing]

315
00:17:43,791 --> 00:17:46,833
Shizu, you can rest in peace.

316
00:17:54,125 --> 00:17:56,833
[SHIZU'S VOICE]
Thank you, Mister Slime.

317
00:19:34,291 --> 00:19:35,708
[MAN]
How could this happen?

318
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:39,333
After I was so close
to being summoned.

319
00:19:39,416 --> 00:19:42,166
And then to have my own family
beat me to the punch.

320
00:19:43,583 --> 00:19:45,333
Next time...

321
00:19:45,416 --> 00:19:47,416
Next time I will not fail.

322
00:19:48,416 --> 00:19:50,833
He will be the one
to lead me.

323
00:19:50,916 --> 00:19:53,958
Perhaps he'll be able to show me
the truth of this world.

324
00:19:54,041 --> 00:19:55,833
[laughing]

325
00:20:02,708 --> 00:20:03,791
[KIDS crying]

326
00:20:03,875 --> 00:20:05,916
Please, don't leave.

327
00:20:06,000 --> 00:20:06,916
We'll miss you.

328
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:08,541
Stop that.

329
00:20:08,625 --> 00:20:11,125
Teach has to go back home,
he can't stay with us.

330
00:20:11,208 --> 00:20:14,000
That's right.
Just get going already!

331
00:20:14,083 --> 00:20:15,458
-But I...
-[RIMURU sighs]

332
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:19,875
♪

333
00:20:21,958 --> 00:20:22,916
They're all yours.

334
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:25,666
Yeah. I'll watch over them.

335
00:20:30,958 --> 00:20:32,125
Teach, wait!

336
00:20:35,708 --> 00:20:37,541
[crying]

337
00:20:39,041 --> 00:20:42,208
[KENYA]
Chloe, you're such a crybaby!

338
00:20:42,291 --> 00:20:43,208
Cut it out!

339
00:20:43,291 --> 00:20:44,958
You're crying, too, Ken.

340
00:20:45,041 --> 00:20:46,916
Nuh-uh! I'm sweating
from my eyeballs!

341
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:49,666
[CHLOE]
Don't leave. Stay here.

342
00:20:49,750 --> 00:20:50,791
[RIMURU]
Hmm.

343
00:20:53,791 --> 00:20:54,833
I can't.

344
00:20:55,833 --> 00:20:58,000
But it'll be okay.

345
00:20:58,083 --> 00:20:59,958
What if I give you
this mask to keep?

346
00:21:00,041 --> 00:21:01,500
[BOTH gasp]

347
00:21:01,583 --> 00:21:04,375
I wanted him to give me that!

348
00:21:04,458 --> 00:21:05,541
But he gave it to me.

349
00:21:05,625 --> 00:21:07,291
Man, lucky!

350
00:21:07,375 --> 00:21:08,916
That's not fair!

351
00:21:09,000 --> 00:21:12,041
[RIMURU] Relax, I have gifts
for you guys, too.

352
00:21:12,125 --> 00:21:13,833
[chuckles]

353
00:21:15,833 --> 00:21:17,500
Whoa!
[laughs]

354
00:21:17,583 --> 00:21:19,458
Aw, man, you look awesome!

355
00:21:19,541 --> 00:21:20,875
Yeah, so do you.

356
00:21:20,958 --> 00:21:22,291
These robes are amazing.

357
00:21:22,375 --> 00:21:24,750
We look so cute!

358
00:21:24,833 --> 00:21:28,416
My friend Shuna's really good
at sewing clothes and stuff.

359
00:21:28,500 --> 00:21:30,291
So she made these
just for you.

360
00:21:30,375 --> 00:21:31,541
That's cool!

361
00:21:31,625 --> 00:21:32,833
Thanks so much.

362
00:21:32,916 --> 00:21:33,833
[RIMURU]
Listen up.

363
00:21:33,916 --> 00:21:36,083
No slacking off on your studies.

364
00:21:36,166 --> 00:21:37,625
This isn't really goodbye.

365
00:21:37,708 --> 00:21:39,791
I'm sure we'll all meet
again someday.

366
00:21:41,458 --> 00:21:43,916
Ranga and I can visit
in our free time.

367
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:46,333
[RANGA] Be sure to dedicate
yourselves to studying,

368
00:21:46,416 --> 00:21:47,416
even after we're gone.

369
00:21:47,500 --> 00:21:48,875
Fine.

370
00:21:48,958 --> 00:21:50,375
But you'd better not forget
to come and see us!

371
00:21:50,458 --> 00:21:52,791
Also, maybe after
we all graduate,

372
00:21:52,875 --> 00:21:54,666
we can come visit you
in your country.

373
00:21:54,750 --> 00:21:56,708
Sure. Sounds good.

374
00:21:56,791 --> 00:22:00,166
I know everyone in my city
will welcome you with open arms.

375
00:22:00,250 --> 00:22:01,708
♪

376
00:22:05,458 --> 00:22:07,291
-See ya!
-Safe travels!

377
00:22:07,375 --> 00:22:09,833
-[ALICE] Take care now!
-[GALE] We'll see you later!

378
00:22:09,916 --> 00:22:11,500
Take care, kids!

379
00:22:17,666 --> 00:22:18,708
Goodbye.

380
00:22:23,458 --> 00:22:26,791
[RANGA] Master, why did you give
Chloe your special mask?

381
00:22:26,875 --> 00:22:30,000
Oh. To be honest,
I'm not really sure.

382
00:22:33,708 --> 00:22:36,125
It sounds kinda weird, I know.

383
00:22:36,208 --> 00:22:37,791
But in the end,
giving the mask to Chloe

384
00:22:37,875 --> 00:22:40,333
felt like
the natural thing to do.

385
00:22:40,416 --> 00:22:42,875
And I think it was for the best.

386
00:22:42,958 --> 00:22:44,208
[RANGA]
I see.

387
00:22:44,291 --> 00:22:46,291
[RIMURU] I bet
if Shizu could have chosen,

388
00:22:46,375 --> 00:22:49,916
she would have preferred that
Chloe had it over me, anyway.

389
00:22:50,000 --> 00:22:52,708
Plus, I'm sure
she'll take good care of it.

390
00:22:52,791 --> 00:22:55,416
Maybe Chloe will follow
in Shizu's footsteps.

391
00:22:55,500 --> 00:22:57,083
She could grow up
to be a Champion,

392
00:22:57,166 --> 00:22:58,541
or maybe even a Hero.

393
00:22:58,625 --> 00:22:59,583
[RANGA]
Perhaps.

394
00:22:59,666 --> 00:23:01,958
[RANGA and RIMURU laugh]

395
00:23:02,041 --> 00:23:03,166
Ranga?

396
00:23:03,250 --> 00:23:05,125
[RANGA]
What is it, Master?

397
00:23:05,208 --> 00:23:08,125
I'm ready to go home.
To our town.

398
00:23:08,208 --> 00:23:10,375
Everyone's waiting.

399
00:23:10,458 --> 00:23:12,208
♪

400
00:23:13,666 --> 00:23:15,708
[howls]

401
00:23:20,625 --> 00:23:22,083
[RIMURU]
There once was a middle-aged man

402
00:23:22,166 --> 00:23:24,750
who lived a perfectly
ordinary life in Japan.

403
00:23:24,833 --> 00:23:26,291
But then he was
stabbed to death,

404
00:23:26,375 --> 00:23:29,000
and so he was reincarnated
in a new world.

405
00:23:30,875 --> 00:23:33,125
He absorbed
the Storm Dragon Veldora,

406
00:23:33,208 --> 00:23:36,791
as well as the body and will of
a powerful Champion named Shizu.

407
00:23:36,875 --> 00:23:38,625
He overcame many challenges

408
00:23:38,708 --> 00:23:41,291
and brought together
monsters of all races.

409
00:23:41,375 --> 00:23:45,250
He built a nation and saved
children from an early grave.

410
00:23:45,333 --> 00:23:48,375
His name is Rimuru Tempest.

411
00:23:48,458 --> 00:23:50,750
And he is not
a bad slime. Slurp.

412
00:23:52,958 --> 00:23:56,708
[GREAT SAGE] Next time,
"Extra: Black and a Mask."

